<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Support on OONI: Open Observatory of Network Interference</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/</link><description>Recent content in Support on OONI: Open Observatory of Network Interference</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>sw</language><atom:link href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Maswali Yanayoulizwa Mara kwa Mara (MYM)</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Hati hiyo imetafsiriwa kwa Kiswahili na &lt;a href="https://zainafoundationtz.org/"&gt;Zaina Foundation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hati asili: &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/support/faq"&gt;Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kipengele hiki kimelenga kuonyesha Maswali Yanayoulizwa Mara kwa Mara (MYM) na jamii.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kuna maswali mengine ambayo ungependa tuyajibu? Tafadhali
&lt;a href="https://ooni.org/about/#contact"&gt;tujulishe&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/#kuhusu-ooni"&gt;Kuhusu OONI&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/#ooni-ni-nini"&gt;Nini maana ya OONI?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/#kwa-nini-ooni"&gt;Kwa nini OONI?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/#ooni-inafanya-nini"&gt;OONI inafanya nini?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/#kwa-nini-kupima-udhibiti-wa-mtandao"&gt;Kwa nini kupima udhibiti wa mtandao?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/#ni-kwa-namna-gani-ooni-inafadhiliwa"&gt;Ni kwa namna gani OONI inafadhiliwa?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/#kuna-uhusiano-gani-kati-ya-ooni-na-tor"&gt;Kuna uhusiano gani kati ya OONI na Tor?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/#ooni-inapatikana-wapi"&gt;OONI inapatikana wapi?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/#ooni-inatambulika-kisheria"&gt;OONI inatambulika kisheria?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/faq/#ni-kwa-namna-gani-naweza-kujihusisha-na-ooni"&gt;Ni kwa namna gani naweza kujihusisha na OONI?&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>OONI Faharasa</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;Hati hiyo imetafsiriwa kwa Kiswahili na &lt;a href="https://zainafoundationtz.org/"&gt;Zaina Foundation&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Hati asili: &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/support/glossary"&gt;OONI Glossary&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Faharasa hii &lt;em&gt;imekusanya&lt;/em&gt; maelezo mafupi ya maneno yaliyotumika kwenye programu ya OONI, njia na tafiti za taarifa.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Kama ungependa kufahamu maneno ya ziada katika faharasa hii tafadhali &lt;a href="https://github.com/ooni/ooni.org"&gt;fungua hapa&lt;/a&gt; au
&lt;a href="https://ooni.org/about/#contact"&gt;tutumie barua pepe&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#api"&gt;API&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#as"&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#asn"&gt;ASN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#bgp"&gt;BGP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#orodha-iliyozuiliwa"&gt;Orodha iliyozuiliwa&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#kurasa-iliyozuiliwa"&gt;Kurasa iliyozuiliwa&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#kuweka-akiba"&gt;Kuweka akiba&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#vifaa-vya-kukwepa-udhibiti-wa-mtandao"&gt;Vifaa vya kukwepa udhibiti wa mtandao&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#mtumiaji"&gt;Mtumiaji&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#mfumo-unaochakata-data"&gt;Mfumo unaochakata data&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#dns"&gt;DNS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#utekaji-wa-dns"&gt;Utekaji wa DNS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#utambuzi-wa-dns"&gt;Utambuzi wa DNS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/glossary/#ombi-la-dns"&gt;Maswali ya DNS&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Seti ya huduma ya OONI</title><link>https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/ooni-outreach-kit/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://ooni.github.io/sw/support/ooni-outreach-kit/</guid><description>&lt;div&gt;
 &lt;a href="https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-outreach-kit/images/image1.png"&gt;
 &lt;img
 src="https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-outreach-kit/images/image1_hu_93fae33066139f61.png"

 
 srcset="https://ooni.github.io/support/ooni-outreach-kit/images/image1_hu_71f0424fbedc3acd.png 2x"
 
 
 title="OONI Outreach Kit"
 
 alt="OONI Outreach Kit"
 
 /&gt;
 &lt;/a&gt;
 
&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Ushiriki wa jamii ni moyo wa kazi za OONI, kama &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/data/"&gt;OONI data&lt;/a&gt; kwenye udhibiti wa mtandao inategemea na upimaji wa watu &lt;a href="https://ooni.org/install/"&gt;OONI Probe&lt;/a&gt; ulimwenguni.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Umevutiwa kushirikisha jamii yako na kipimo cha udhibiti cha OONI?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Seti ya huduma ya OONI inajumuisha &lt;strong&gt;nyenzo ambazo unavutiwa kuzitumia&lt;/strong&gt; kama sehemu ya juhudi za ushiriki za jumuiya ya OONI.&lt;/p&gt;
